description: Stunning Eastside Penthouse Duplex on the second and third floor of a classic South Boston Rowhouse with private Roof Deck! Main living level features a sunny, open living concept with high ceilings, bay window, hardwood floors, exposed brick and landing flowing seamlessly to your private full staircase leading to private roof deck with city and water views. Large chef's kitchen has stainless appliances, gas cooking, and new quartz countertops. The first level features two large, equal bedrooms, one with bay window and alcove, both with exposed brick accents, a full bath and a landing off of the master.  A/C, Mini-Split and Laundry in Unit. Roof, decks, hatch and outside rear staircase new as of 2022. Prime Eastside location near M Street Beach and Broadway shops and restaurants.
